Design a loan eligibility decision tree:

DECISION TREE: Loan Eligibility Engine

```
                    [START]
                       |
              [Loan Type?]
             /     |      \
      Personal  Mortgage   Auto
          |        |         |
     [Amount?] [Amount?]  [Amount?]
      /    \     /    \     /    \
   <10k  >10k  <200k >200k  <30k  >30k
     |     |     |     |      |     |
  [Simple][Standard][Standard][Premium][Simple][Standard]
   Eval    Eval     Eval     Eval    Eval    Eval
```

---

LEVEL 1: Loan Type Classification

```json
{
  "node": "loan_type",
  "prompt": "Based on the application, classify the loan type",
  "branches": [
    {
      "value": "personal",
      "criteria": "Unsecured personal loan, general purpose",
      "next": "personal_amount"
    },
    {
      "value": "mortgage",
      "criteria": "Home purchase or refinance, property as collateral",
      "next": "mortgage_amount"
    },
    {
      "value": "auto",
      "criteria": "Vehicle purchase, vehicle as collateral",
      "next": "auto_amount"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

LEVEL 2: Amount Thresholds

Personal Loan Branch:
```json
{
  "node": "personal_amount",
  "branches": [
    {
      "condition": "amount < 10000",
      "next": "personal_simple_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score"],
      "description": "Quick approval path"
    },
    {
      "condition": "amount >= 10000 AND amount < 50000",
      "next": "personal_standard_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score", "employment_history", "debt_ratio"],
      "description": "Standard evaluation"
    },
    {
      "condition": "amount >= 50000",
      "next": "personal_premium_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score", "employment_history", "debt_ratio", "assets", "tax_returns"],
      "description": "Full underwriting required"
    }
  ]
}
```

Mortgage Branch:
```json
{
  "node": "mortgage_amount",
  "branches": [
    {
      "condition": "amount < 200000",
      "next": "mortgage_standard_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score", "employment_history", "debt_ratio", "property_value", "down_payment"]
    },
    {
      "condition": "amount >= 200000 AND amount < 500000",
      "next": "mortgage_standard_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score", "employment_history", "debt_ratio", "property_value", "down_payment", "assets"]
    },
    {
      "condition": "amount >= 500000",
      "next": "mortgage_jumbo_eval",
      "required_data": ["income", "credit_score", "employment_history", "debt_ratio", "property_value", "down_payment", "assets", "tax_returns", "investment_accounts"],
      "description": "Jumbo loan - additional scrutiny"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

LEVEL 3: Leaf Node Evaluations

Personal Simple Evaluation:
```json
{
  "node": "personal_simple_eval",
  "type": "leaf",
  "ai_prompt": "Evaluate this small personal loan application using simplified criteria.",
  "scoring_rules": {
    "credit_score": {
      "weight": 60,
      "thresholds": {
        "excellent": {"min": 720, "score": 100},
        "good": {"min": 680, "score": 80},
        "fair": {"min": 620, "score": 60},
        "poor": {"min": 0, "score": 30}
      }
    },
    "income_to_payment_ratio": {
      "weight": 40,
      "thresholds": {
        "excellent": {"max_ratio": 0.10, "score": 100},
        "good": {"max_ratio": 0.20, "score": 80},
        "acceptable": {"max_ratio": 0.30, "score": 60}
      }
    }
  },
  "decision_thresholds": {
    "auto_approve": 80,
    "manual_review": 60,
    "auto_decline": 60
  },
  "output": {
    "decision": "approved|review|declined",
    "score": 85,
    "reasons": ["Excellent credit score", "Low payment ratio"],
    "conditions": ["Rate: 8.5%", "Term: 36 months"]
  }
}
```

Mortgage Jumbo Evaluation:
```json
{
  "node": "mortgage_jumbo_eval",
  "type": "leaf",
  "ai_prompt": "Perform comprehensive evaluation for jumbo mortgage application.",
  "scoring_rules": {
    "credit_score": {"weight": 25, "min_required": 700},
    "debt_to_income": {"weight": 25, "max_allowed": 0.43},
